<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Agent Application Received - CarRental</title>
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        
        body {
            font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #374151;
            background-color: #f9fafb;
        }
        
        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 12px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }
        
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #A11312, #8a0f0e);
            color: white;
            padding: 40px 30px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        
        .header h1 {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .header p {
            font-size: 16px;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        
        .content {
            padding: 40px 30px;
        }
        
        .greeting {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        
        .message {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            line-height: 1.7;
        }
        
        .application-details {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
            border-left: 4px solid #A11312;
        }
        
        .application-details h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #1a1a1a;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .detail-item {
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
        }
        
        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #374151;
            min-width: 120px;
        }
        
        .detail-value {
            color: #6b7280;
        }
        
        .next-steps {
            background-color: #fef2f2;
            border: 1px solid #fecaca;
            border-radius: 8px;
            padding: 25px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }
        
        .next-steps h3 {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #A11312;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }
        
        .steps-list {
            list-style: none;
        }
        
        .steps-list li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            color: #A11312;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 25px;
        }
        
        .steps-list li:before {
            content: "â†’";
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            color: #8a0f0e;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        
        .footer {
            background-color: #f8fafc;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .footer p {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6b7280;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        .contact-info {
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 15px;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 6px;
            border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }
        
        .contact-info p {
            margin-bottom: 5px;
            font-size: 14px;
        }
        
        .logo {
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }
        
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 10px;
                border-radius: 8px;
            }
            
            .header, .content, .footer {
                padding: 20px;
            }
            
            .header h1 {
                font-size: 24px;
            }
            
            .detail-item {
                flex-direction: column;
                align-items: flex-start;
            }
            
            .detail-label {
                min-width: auto;
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <div class="logo">ðŸš— CarRental</div>
            <h1>Agent Application Received</h1>
            <p>Thank you for your interest in becoming a CarRental agent</p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="content">
            <div class="greeting">
                Hello <%= name %>! ðŸ‘‹
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                Thank you for submitting your application to become a CarRental agent! 
                We've received your application and our team will review it carefully.
            </div>
            
            <div class="application-details">
                <h3>Application Details</h3>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Applicant:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= name %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Email:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= email %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Application Date:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= applicationDate %></span>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-item">
                    <span class="detail-label">Application ID:</span>
                    <span class="detail-value"><%= applicationId %></span>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="next-steps">
                <h3>What happens next?</h3>
                <ul class="steps-list">
                    <li>Our admin team will review your application</li>
                    <li>We'll verify your information and credentials</li>
                    <li>You'll receive an email with our decision within 3-5 business days</li>
                    <li>If approved, you'll get access to list your vehicles</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <div class="message">
                While you wait, you can continue using CarRental as a customer to explore our platform 
                and understand how the rental process works from a user's perspective.
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <p>Best regards,</p>
            <p><strong>The CarRental Team</strong></p>
            
            <div class="contact-info">
                <h4>Need Help?</h4>
                <p>Email: carrent@info.com</p>
                <p>Phone: 0768163367</p>
            </div>
            
            <p style="margin-top: 20px; font-size: 12px; color: #9ca3af;">
                This email was sent to <%= email %>. If you didn't submit an agent application, please contact our support team.
            </p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html> 